1.title: Tiled Sails and an Arch of Iron
1.plot: In this first video of Sydney in 3D we see the city from the Northern side of Sydney Harbour, then catch a ferry across to Circular Quay, with views of the famous Harbour Bridge and stunning Sydney Opera House as we travel.

2.title: A Waterside Walk to the Windy Willows
2.plot: Darling Harbour is a place of contrasts and one of my favourite places for relaxation in Sydney. Just a short walk downhill from the city's main shopping centre, it is the ideal location for a waterside lunch or evening meal. In fact historians tell us that people have been eating seafood at this location since long before the pyramids were built! But a lot has changed since that time.
